= Tabaré Vázqoez = Mntocing hngkawas 1940 idas 1 jiyax 17 ka Tabaré Vázqoez ga, empklaw ka hiya. Bokong klwaan Urogoay ta sayang o kiya ka Tabaré Vázqoez, pnaah hngkawas 2015 idas 3 jiyax 1 pnrajing kmlawa klwaan.
